@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.exp(((tmp + 0.94 - tmp + 0.72) - (v2 + 0.69 / v1 + 0.69)))
    tmp = v1
    v0 = (((tmp + 0.15 * v1 + 0.05) + (v1 + 0.96 - v1 + 0.24)) / wp.exp(tmp))
